{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_26","type":"agent_message","text":"The current frontend only knows the coarse job counters, while the backend already persists narration segments and per-segment assets. I’m checking how much of that is available in hydration now so I can expose trust-building detail without inventing ephemeral client state."}}
