{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_42","type":"agent_message","text":"There isn’t a browser-facing audio asset URL yet, so I’m checking the storage layer before deciding whether to expose preview playback now or leave it gated behind “available when a stream URL exists.” I want to avoid baking in a fake client-only URL that will be wrong once export endpoints land."}}
