{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_251","type":"agent_message","text":"Implemented the audio preview and segment-status stage end to end. The backend now hydrates narration segments plus preview assets and browser-playable `public_url`s, the frontend audio stage shows durable render state, remaining work, per-segment status with inline checkpoint players, and a clearly separate compiled-master player, and realtime audio job events now trigger snapshot refreshes so new preview clips appear without a reload.\n\nI also fixed a real desktop layout issue discovered during browser QA: the inherited sticky side-summary pattern overflowed the fixed-width stage pane, so the audio stage now uses a stacked layout and single-column segment cards. The code changes are committed at `6dd8169` with `feat(prompt-76): audio preview and segment status ui`. The required reviewer summary was written last to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/76_audio_preview_and_segment_status_ui/summary.md).\n\nVerification passed with backend tests, frontend tests, lint, build, and browser captures. Browser QA had to use a local fallback stack because Docker Desktop was unavailable; that detail is documented in the summary. Visual artifacts are at [prompt-76-audio-stage-desktop-status-panel.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-76-audio-stage-desktop-status-panel.png), [prompt-76-audio-stage-desktop-summary.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-76-audio-stage-desktop-summary.png), and [prompt-76-audio-stage-mobile-viewport.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-76-audio-stage-mobile-viewport.png). The only non-blocking verification note is the existing Vite chunk-size warning during `frontend` build."}}
